OL,3,CMan admits harassing Blackpool South MP
OL,5,FA man has admitted harassing the
OL,6,FBlackpool South MP Chris Webb.
OL,8,FLancashire Police received a report
OL,9,Fearlier in July that emails containing
OL,10,Fthreatening and abusive messages had
OL,11,Fbeen received by the Labour MP.
OL,13,FAhmet Hilal, 41, of Red Bank Road,
OL,14,FBlackpool, was charged with harassment
OL,15,F(putting a person in fear of violence)
OL,16,Fbetween June 6 and July 14, police
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FHilal appeared before Lancaster
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday, where
OL,21,Fhe pleaded guilty.
